      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">A 48-year-old policy maker is evaluating different indices to understand the overall health status of a population in a particular region. He comes across the Physical Quality of Life Index (PQLI) and wants to understand its components and utilization better. Which of the following statements about the PQLI is NOT true?</span></p>",
